# 🧠 3. Types of Arrays

## What is it

Different structures of arrays.

---

## Key Components

### Single-Dimensional
Linear storage

### Multi-Dimensional
Table/matrix-like storage

---

## How to Answer (Interview Style)

Java supports single-dimensional and multi-dimensional arrays for different data storage needs.

---

## Practical Example

```java
