# 🧠 5. Traversing Arrays ⭐

## What is it

Accessing array elements sequentially.

---

## Key Components

- for loop
- enhanced for loop
- Index traversal

---

## How to Answer (Interview Style)

Arrays are traversed using loops to access and process individual elements.

---

## Practical Example

```java
for(int i=0; i<arr.length; i++) {
   System.out.println(arr[i]);
}
```

---

## Common Mistakes

- Wrong loop conditions
- Index errors

---

## Expected Interview Questions

- How to traverse arrays?
- Difference between for and enhanced for?
- Common traversal mistakes?

