# 🧠 8. Arrays vs ArrayList ⭐

## What is it

Comparison between fixed and dynamic collections.

---

## Key Components

### Arrays
Fixed size

### ArrayList
Dynamic size

---

## How to Answer (Interview Style)

Arrays have fixed size, while ArrayList supports dynamic resizing and provides built-in utility methods.

---

## Practical Example

```java
ArrayList<String> list =
new ArrayList<>();
```

---

## Common Mistakes

- Using arrays for dynamic data

